               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Māryām “Miracles of Mary”&#xD; I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah and hymns
                     (fols. 5ra-8rb)&#xD; I-2) Introductory exhortation (fols. 8rb-9rb)&#xD; I-3)
                     ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... "I worship Thee..." (fols. 9rb-9vb)&#xD; I-4)
                     Taʾammǝra Māryām: 81 miracles (fols. 10ra-85ra)&#xD; I-5) ʾAkkonu bǝʾsi... “Does
                     not the man…” (distributed among the Miracles of Mary, fols.
                     11va-35ra)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="5ra" to="105rb"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT2384Taamme"/>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="5ra" to="8rb"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="LIT1968Mashaf"/>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.1">
                           <locus from="7vb" to="8ra">7vb-8ra</locus>
                           <title ref="LIT5442HymnMary">ʾO-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝya qǝddǝst dǝngǝl ba-kǝlʾe Māryām walādita ʾamlāk ... "O my
                              Lady, Holy Two-fold Virgin Mary, Godbearing ..."</title>
                           <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.2">
                           <locus target="#8r">8ra-rb</locus>
                           <title ref="LIT5443Salamlaki2">salām laki ʾo-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝya Māryām ʾǝmmu la-bǝrhān wa-ʾǝmma madḫǝn ...
                              "Salutation to you, o my Lady Mary, Mother of the Light and Mother of the
                              Saviour ..."</title>                        
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">                        
                        <locus from="8rb" to="9rb"/>
                        <title ref="LIT3584Intro">Introductory exhortation</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        
                     </msItem>                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                        <locus from="9rb" to="9vb"/>
