                           laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki ... “I worship Thee ...” </title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     </msItem>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                        <locus from="10ra" to="85ra"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="LIT3585Taamme">81 Miracles of Mary</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>                        
